Dreamy summer evenings at Peggy's Cove, where rugged beauty meets serenity. 🌊✨

Take some time to visit this charming fishing village at sunset when the golden sun dips below the horizon, casting a warm glow on the weathered rocks, making for the most picturesque evening stroll. 🌅🎣 

Make dinner plans before sunset at one of these local eateries:
@tomslobstershack - Known for their variety of lobster rolls and chowder, this spot serves up fresh seafood with vibrant flavour. 🦞✨

@rhubarbrestaurant_ - Dive into a diverse menu full of seasonal comfort foods from the land and sea. This restaurant is particularly great to accommodate gluten-free diets. 🍲🥂 

@souwesterpeggyscove - Enjoy Nova Scotian classics with stunning views of the famed Peggy's Point Lighthouse. 🌊🦞

Who are you taking here? Tag them in the comments!👇

📍 Peggy's Cove, Nova Scotia
📷 @alexstead

